---
title: Quick Louisiana Double Popcorn Chicken Tacos with Cos Salad & Dijon Mayonnaise
description: Taco night means a party for your tastebuds, so let’s celebrate with the best chicken, spiced Louisiana chicken. Get the party started with popping corn and salad, then wind things down by adding a drizzle of creamy dijon mayo. This is going to be a taco night you won’t forget.
